        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " fields, and pairs them with a descriptive text from the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "InvoiceAccountBillingGroupDesc",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " field. The procedure filters records based on specific criteria related to account status, manual data entry flag, and record currency, ensuring only active and current records are considered."
        }
